tika.dc.description: Things are heating up in the village of Turnham Malpas. Now comfortably settled in the Big House, Johnny and Alice Templeton are over the moon at the arrival of their second son. But Johnny’s roguish younger brother, Chris Templeton, is visiting from Brazil and causing not a little trouble in the village.
